130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:42:59.000Z","msg":"你搞得呢個見習律師<br />\n何妖,馬恩國你唔搞？<br />\n<br />\n仆街律政司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f35e2cfb46a68f3ea17c429e29c777e08bdb3f7","tid":1493923,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:51:26.000Z","msg":"前立法會議員、資深大律師梁家傑形容律政司「踩過界」，批評有關行為是「向年輕律師製造白色恐怖」，又向司長鄭若驊放話：<span style=\"color: red;\">「慳啲啦！你咁過份，只會更惹人反感！」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87bf83770f5cb3a201fe056b57fbc12a2501e6a7","tid":1493923,"uid":116198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:54:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">何妖:殺無赦<br />\n律政司:冇事</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e6c06fef1ee61f8e9e978f94801262de95b7fa38","tid":1493923,"uid":70898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:04:29.000Z","msg":"咁何妖呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2a1fdf6f4854381bad1eb3d4ae6a7efc97d8e1","tid":1493923,"uid":85965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87bf83770f5cb3a201fe056b57fbc12a2501e6a7","tid":1493923,"uid":116198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:54:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">何妖:殺無赦<br />\n律政司:冇事</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:08:32.000Z","msg":"完美演繹咩係選擇性控告"},{"pid":"6a205142ecf215baa6b7c5911e5dd6117de4c7ea","tid":1493923,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:11:36.000Z","msg":"其實有冇諗過第二條戰線制裁律政司？"}]}